ss=m><span class=title> Warrior Epic</span><hr size=1> Is it me or are the effects on this somewhat stupid?<br>
<br>
With the 2 handed sword there is a random proc that reduces your hp by 200 or so and lowers you on the aggro list. Well with proper management anyone can stay below the MA in terms of aggro. As for the self damage...<br>
<br>
A similar effect is on one of the single handed swords. Along with a very monk epic type clicky effect on the other sword. All in all these effects seem pretty bad when compared with things like the Ranger epic swords or a Ragebringer.<br>
<br>
Are these effects still like this or have they been changed? <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=28162>Daerv Karasu</a><br><a href=http://www.epic-heroes.com>Epic Heroes</a><br><a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/bepicheroes73161>EH EZBoard</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#1478A2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub88.ezboard.com/upaendragtanreall.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Paendrag Tanreall</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Orc Pawn</span><br>  Posts: 138<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/17/02 12:04:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub88.ezboard.com/fepicheroes73161frm14.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=76.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Warrior Epic</span><hr size=1> Problem is that info comes from the spdat.eff, which can be confusing.  Rage of vallon (main hand sword effect I believe)  Causes a 100Pt DD on the mob and raises the MA's aggro by 500.  It is confusing because in the &quot;old&quot; spdat's, hate's were managed backwards, like it said hate was reduced by 500 on the sword, but a spell like ranger jolt (lower aggro), said it was raised by 500 <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   But those numbers are pulled off of the spdat that is currently in effect right now, the offhand sword effect is <br>
<br>
Increase Dexterity by 40 (L1)<br>
Increase Attack (ATK) by 30 (L1)<br>
Increase Armor Class (AC) by 12 (L1)<br>
<br>
<br>
and the 2 hand sword info is<br>
<br>
Rage of Zek<br>
Decrease Current Hitpoints by 175 (L1)<br>
Raises you on the target's hate list by 500 points<br>
<br>
500 points of hate seems to be a fair amount of hate, combined with taunt and the DD aggro by itself, the warrior epic weapons are taunt machines excluding some of the stupid fast hitting higher end velious and luclin items (which have no taunt proc, but are like 12/17 ratios)<br>
